OL,3,CPolice and probation service 'failed'
OL,4,Cmurdered father of one
OL,6,FVideo report by Anna Youssef
OL,8,FPolice and probation services "failed
OL,9,Fto act on critical information" which
OL,10,Fcould have stopped a dad being
OL,11,Fmurdered and dismembered, his family
OL,12,Fhave said.
OL,14,FAshley Walsh was attacked and killed
OL,15,Fby Gerard McGlacken and his nephew
OL,16,FAaron Evitt at McGlacken's flat in
OL,17,FCollyhurst, Manchester, in January
OL,18,F2022, before his dismembered body was
OL,19,Fdumped in Sandhills Park.
