OL,3,CPolice and probation service 'failed'
OL,4,Cmurdered father of one
OL,6,FAn inquest into his death heard
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police had visited
OL,8,FMcGlacken just weeks before the
OL,9,Fkilling after becoming aware he had
OL,10,Ftried to import an illegal knife,
OL,11,Fbreaching his licence conditions.
OL,13,FBut, when he told an officer about his
OL,14,Flicence during the visit, that
OL,15,Finformation was not included in his
OL,16,Fpolice report, or raised with his
OL,17,Fsuperiors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
