OL,3,CPolice and probation service 'failed'
OL,4,Cmurdered father of one
OL,6,FIt was also told that McGlacken had
OL,7,Fbeen drinking heavily, but while Evitt
OL,8,Freported this to his probation
OL,9,Fofficer, no action had been taken.
OL,11,FDespite saying there had been multiple
OL,12,Ffailings by both Greater Manchester
OL,13,FPolice and the Probation Service,
OL,14,Fcoroner Zak Golombek said it would be
OL,15,Fconjecture to say those failings
OL,16,Fcontributed to Ashley Walsh's death.
OL,18,FHe instead delivered a conclusion of
OL,19,Funlawful killing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
