OL,3,CPolice and probation service 'failed'
OL,4,Cmurdered father of one
OL,6,F"We trusted the system to manage
OL,7,Fdangerous offenders, and for us that
OL,8,Ftrust has been completely broken. No
OL,9,Ffamily should have to go through this
OL,10,Fpain.
OL,12,F"We will continue to fight for change
OL,13,Fso that no other family has to endure
OL,14,Fthe nightmare we have lived through.
OL,16,F"Ashley's memory deserves justice, and
OL,17,Fwe will not stop until we have it."
