OL,3,CPolice and probation service 'failed'
OL,4,Cmurdered father of one
OL,6,FEvidence provided by the Probation
OL,7,FService said that, given their
OL,8,Foffending history, licence conditions
OL,9,Fshould have been included to prevent
OL,10,Fcontact between McGlacken and Evitt,
OL,11,Fas well as to address their substance
OL,12,Fmisuse whilst on licence.
OL,14,FHowever, no such conditions were put
OL,15,Finto place.
OL,17,FMcGlacken was known to GMP and his
OL,18,Fattempt to import an illegal 'gravity
OL,19,Fknife' from China following his
OL,20,Frelease from prison, was investigated
OL,21,Fin the month prior to Ashley's death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
