OL,3,CPolice and probation service 'failed'
OL,4,Cmurdered father of one
OL,6,FGiving evidence at the inquest, the
OL,7,Fofficer said McGlacken told him he was
OL,8,Fon licence when he visited his home in
OL,9,FDecember 2021, but he had no training
OL,10,Fon licences and did not know what the
OL,11,Fterm meant, and as a result had not
OL,12,Fincluded the information in his police
OL,13,Freport.
OL,15,FA senior officer told the inquest that
OL,16,Fas a result he was also unaware of the
OL,17,Flicence when he closed the crime
OL,18,Freport. The Probation Service told the
OL,19,Fcoroner this was information that
OL,20,Fshould have been passed to them.
