OL,6,F"We would also like to thank our legal
OL,7,Fteam at Leigh Day, who fought
OL,8,Ftirelessly to have Ashley's inquest re-
OL,9,Fopened after the criminal trial.
OL,10,FWithout the work of Benjamin Burrows
OL,11,Fand Ellie Sutherland, the full extent
OL,12,Fof the failures leading up to Ashley's
OL,13,Fdeath would never have been shared to
OL,14,Fthe public."
OL,16,FA GMP Spokesperson said: "Our thoughts
OL,17,Fcontinue to be with Ashley's loved
OL,18,Fones who have endured the most
OL,19,Ftraumatic time following his death. It
OL,20,Fis right that his killers will remain
OL,21,Fbehind bars for a long time to come.
