OL,8,Fchanges. We have acknowledged that we
OL,9,Fshould've better shared with probation
OL,10,Finformation about one of the offenders
OL,11,Fprior to Ashley's death.
OL,13,F"At the time of this incident, student
OL,14,Fofficers were trained at the national
OL,15,Fstandard in line with the College of
OL,16,FPolicing curriculum. We have since
OL,17,Fgone beyond this standard to ensure
OL,18,Fall current and future student
OL,19,Fofficers will be educated about the
OL,20,Frole of probation and our offender
OL,21,Fmanagement units.
